DATES AND TIMES

NOW() - returns the system dat and time of the server
CURDATE() - returns system date without the time
CURTIME() - returns system time without the date

NOW() - using for adding a timestamp when a row is being added to the database

DAY - gives day of the month
DAYNAME - gives name of the day of the week
DAYOFMONTH - same as DAY
DAYOFWEEK - give number corresponding to the day. Sunday is 1, Saturday is 7
DAYOFYEAR - give day if we were countin from Jan 1st as 1

MONTH(NOW())
MONTHNAME(NOW())

DAY(NOW())

UTC

set time_zone = '-4:00'
set GLOBAL time_zone = '-4:00'
